{"tid":376241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【虛報學歷】民建聯柯創盛報稱英國碩士學歷　大學指無同名學生紀錄","createTime":"2017-08-26T23:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T00:05:37.000Z","uid":131691,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e12f024771b5f975404cc5e966ab777bc178c8b1","tid":376241,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:28:34.000Z","msg":"民建聯立法會九龍東候選人柯創盛近日就碩士學歷問題在網上澄清，自己透過一間名為「Raffles Academy - World Education Council」修讀英國諾丁漢特倫特大學（Nottingham Trent University）的工商管理碩士課程及畢業，不過該大學昨日接受本報查詢時指出，其學生紀錄系統並無名為「Or Chong-shing」或「Or Chong-shing Wilson」的學生，對於校方會否調查事件，發言人指無補充。<br />\n<br />\n大學發言人又指出，該校曾與「Raffles Academy」簽訂認證服務合約（validation service agreement），合約期至2013年12月屆滿。<br />\n本報昨天多次致電及短訊柯創盛，但未有回應，其選舉代理人林亨利今晚電話回應本報查詢時稱，柯就其學歷問題已多次在選舉論壇及facebook回應，惟無正面回應為何英國諾丁漢特倫特大學指沒有柯創盛的學生紀錄。林重申柯手持的文件包括成績表均為正本，但未有回應會否向本報出示其學歷證明。<br />\n柯創盛在民建聯競選網站報稱學歷為碩士，但無列出畢業院校，他上周於facbeook拍片再澄清時手持該課程畢業證書，指自己於2010年入讀，至2013年畢業，但因拍攝距離較遠及解像度不足，無法看清證書內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160825/s00001/1472136388377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160825%2Fs00001%2F1472136388377&d=Z6mWvjkh4U%2FzXuqpUJjLFP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e07f35b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160825%2Fs00001%2F1472136388377&h=984fe2a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160825/s00001/1472136388377</a>"},{"pid":"e8a499ce2e99ee93c93f768275c8f10d8f9bbc6c","tid":376241,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:31:18.000Z","msg":"野雞都唔幫佢"},{"pid":"2cdb939c897762d7c5737a258dd0404f463e5065","tid":376241,"uid":27024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:32:29.000Z","msg":"又要binc 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e36489c1f23ad2be9aa8bca6e1edc8fd7ed1425","tid":376241,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:35:57.000Z","msg":"份人CC叔叔做乜姐，有讀過又駛乜怕認呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌"},{"pid":"f93ac90adb0b56d89faf74ae29388a2ec03f626f","tid":376241,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:46:11.000Z","msg":"有冇犯法"},{"pid":"724c399e1011472817cd06b9fb4541c7c8a0784e","tid":376241,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:52:11.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"69a8cb2428072a08710240973ed1eb6b44d46c2d","tid":376241,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇犯法</blockquote><br />\n民建聯<br />\n你話呢"}]}